The '''Soldier''', also known as the '''Sentry''', is an enemy in the original ''[[Final Fantasy]]''. It is a moderately powerful enemy at the time it is fought, but can be dealt with [[Lightning (Final Fantasy)|Lightning]]-elemental items and spells, or a constant barrage of physical attacks.

